<item>
            <title>[FELIX-347] New Maven SCR Plugin does not emit namespace declaration on JDK 1.4</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-347</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Java 1.4 Transformer used by the Maven SCR Plugin seems to no emit the namespace declaration needed to parse the scr descriptors containing namespaces. Java 5 and newer transformers work alright.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The workaround is to manually create the namespace declaration as an attribute to the root element. This workaround has been tested on JDK 1.4, 5 and 6.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
